---
layout: default
---

#left-column
  - unless page.hide_title
    %h1.pagetitle #{page.title}
  ~ content
#right-column
  %h1 Latest stable release
  #latest-release
    BoxGrinder Build:
    %a{:href=>"#{announcement_for_version('0.8.0').url}"}
      = latest_release[:version]
  %h1 Latest posts
  #latest-posts
    - for post in site.posts[0,4] do
      .item
        %h5
          %a{:href=>post.url}= post.title
        %h6 #{post.date.strftime( '%d %B %Y' )}
    #even-more
      %a{:href=>'/blog'}More blog posts
  %h1 Cool stuff
  #cool-stuff
    :markdown
      [Desktop wallpaper](http://www.jboss.org/coolstuff/desktopwallpapers/boxgrinder.html) | [Project Swag](http://www.cafepress.com/jbossorg/7089670)